{"tid":2278981,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個當時好影響自己嘅藉口，後尾先發現係大話","createTime":"2020-11-09T12:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T05:43:48.000Z","uid":307910,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ef089631b5bc511e588f8b10b5073dc0aa037e","tid":2278981,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:54:58.000Z","msg":"當時我鍾意咗一個女仔，咁佢就大我幾個月<br />\n<br />\n我記得當時所有追佢嘅男仔都會畀佢叫做哥哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哥～哥！！！ <br />\n（把聲真係好sweet)<br />\n不過唔同嘅係，我同佢係會互相叫大家全名<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個衰妹成日姣到仆街，高八度咁喺走廊嗌我全名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n怕醜到我即刻扮聽唔到跑入班房<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想可以做哥哥咁，可以lead住呢個妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然個女仔只係大我幾個月，而且我嗰時都係高過佢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當時覺得同佢好夾，忍唔住同咗佢表白<br />\n然之後佢同我講，話覺得我太細個，所以唔想同我一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時好鍾意呢個女仔，好嬲自己點解唔早啲出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知！！！去到最後佢同咗個同我同一個月出世嘅男仔一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但知道之後真係無嬲，純粹係覺得自己好on9，點解會信咗呢句說話成兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51b2bde89e6341565f2b4691796b83c1157501b","tid":2278981,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:55:18.000Z","msg":"冇錯 就係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aec493b5b7d01021a7764f7cb911aa6655b4953","tid":2278981,"uid":303436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"K小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a36487208fa0fb70650f67c5aa061721d8b223","tid":2278981,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aec493b5b7d01021a7764f7cb911aa6655b4953","tid":2278981,"uid":303436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"K小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:59:29.000Z","msg":"真感激你用18秒鐘看看信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d766cefa37c28b32b4a2a7bd47f88bb3688b3ee8","tid":2278981,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"おにいじゃん～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15475fb7fae65172f91ca64d6c7667db1ff36dd","tid":2278981,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d766cefa37c28b32b4a2a7bd47f88bb3688b3ee8","tid":2278981,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"おにいじゃん～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"幾pure<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係心都融埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84ca47207136682ee3d2527337b31364add88ee","tid":2278981,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f15475fb7fae65172f91ca64d6c7667db1ff36dd","tid":2278981,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d766cefa37c28b32b4a2a7bd47f88bb3688b3ee8","tid":2278981,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"おにいじゃん～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"幾pure<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係心都融埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim