:09.000Z","msg":"好慘豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdc562f6b9ab41500b99f950475ea6d198011f5","tid":2278981,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T02:43:30.000Z","msg":"尋晚又夢到kelly<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  夢入面嘅佢變成長直髮，係我啱啱識佢嘅時候嘅髮型，然後我係咁捉住佢隻手，係咁叫佢原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然佢冇揈開我隻手，但之後我好似都係係咁求佢，但佢都係無理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我就扎醒咗，之後又訓返，就無再見到佢，同屋企人一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係不停咁諗住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但已經見唔反佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076d1e27aa5728fc369084ae51e52cee2a8870f4","tid":2278981,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb178917fcaedd5705e4d6bce46e0bf4af811c66","tid":2278981,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"580b20a34af15f44b5d8b14a65a845913d6c693b","tid":2278981,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c84ca47207136682ee3d2527337b31364add88ee","tid":2278981,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:21:34.000Z","msg":"樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？ 係咪引鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T04:22:08.000Z","msg":"尋晚同你講起佢 本身已經忘記得7788<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290d7f91cd2778d38a4f289380fa6787db364154","tid":2278981,"uid":350206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score