1-10T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93aa0dec3af50c549ccdd894adacee2e380fbca","tid":2278981,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8f5da84f10776b34bc6fb536a773165b3338a32","tid":2278981,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c4333889b8eb3e2729fc416d7bfa752ba68a3c8","tid":2278981,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b4a683e0bdf78811218e7af788fa578c0595248","tid":2278981,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:27:45.000Z","msg":"真係除？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都明 如果心入面有個好重要嘅人真係幾靚都冇feel"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T10:06:52.000Z","msg":"唔係真係除啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全唔想睇 心霖 你彈開啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T16:45:50.000Z","msg":"嫌棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1845bb8ff372c05c91949f1ff35b6dfa288eece7","tid":2278981,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T18:05:12.000Z","msg":"我未返到屋企。<br />\n<br />\n細個冇乜同學同我住同區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當時真係好想好似其他同學咁有得放學去人地屋企玩<br />\n隔離位個同學知道就即刻話：咁啱啊！我住你樓上！<br />\n：3樓啊？<br />\n：係呀！<br />\n：今日放學我上你屋企玩啊<br />\n跟著上到去禁門鍾，出黎嘅係平時成日係出面放狗嗰個啊叔同啊嬸(尷)，個同學就唔見影<br />\n<br />\n第二日返到學校問隔離同學<br />\n：喂我琴日上到你屋企禁鍾，你唔係到嘅？<br />\n：我未返到屋企啊<br />\n：咁你今日放學有冇野做<br />\n：冇喎<br />\n：咁我今日遲少少再去禁你門鍾啦<br />\n<br />\n我禁左3次門鍾先知比人fake左<br />\n直到某一次問其他同學先知佢住第二到<br />\n再問屋企人  樓上根本冇小學雞<br />\n雖然係我細個好蠢好易信人<br />\n但真係好多謝佢增加左我對男性嘅不信任感<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">真係柒到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7dd1cc8c0713f0bf794157c39ceef8d205ee8ca5","tid":2278981,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1845bb8ff372c05c91949f1ff35b6dfa288eece7","tid":2278981,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T18:05:12.000Z","msg":"我未返到屋企。<br />\n<br />\n細個冇乜同學同我住同區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當時真係好想好似其他同學咁有得放學去人地屋企玩<br />\n隔離位個同學知道就即刻話：咁啱啊！我住你樓上！<br />\n：3樓啊？<br />\n：係呀！<br />\n：今日放學我上你屋企玩啊<br />\n跟著上到去禁門鍾，出黎嘅係平時成日係出面放狗嗰個啊叔同啊嬸(尷)，個同學就唔見影<br />\n<br />\n第二日返到學校問隔離同學<br />\n：喂我琴日上到你屋企禁鍾，你唔係到嘅？<br />\n：我未返到屋企啊<br />\n：咁你今日放學有冇野做<br />\n：冇喎<br />\n：咁我今日遲少少再去禁你門鍾啦<br />\n<br />\n我禁左3次門鍾先知比人fake左<br />\n直到某一次問其他同學先知佢住第二到<br />\n再問屋企人  樓上根本冇小學雞<br />\n雖然係我細個好蠢好易信人<br />\n但真係好多謝佢增加左我對男性嘅不信任感<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">真係柒到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}